{"tid":1308071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一係守連儂牆，一係守住香港","createTime":"2019-07-11T19:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T14:55:50.000Z","uid":216008,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f6b09e56b5fb9fdbc2f2768750660973e9ba8b","tid":1308071,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:46:11.000Z","msg":"連儂牆，從來都唔係一件藝術作品，但我見手足非常愛惜佢，咁姑且當佢係藝術品，而佢絕對係屬於Participatory art：有人起壇，有人寫，有人痴，有人撕。<br />\n如果要從藝術角度去睇佢，就係我地要由得人撕，由得人破壞，因為連儂牆既存在目的，就係比人表達訴求，難聽啲講，破壞連儂牆都係一種訴求既表達。<br />\n我唔係叫你地縱容，只係希望你地以另一個角度睇連儂牆既意義。<br />\n連儂牆遲早會消失，亦都要接受。<br />\n\b幾十張memo紙，一面牆，就已經起到一個連儂牆，但我地既地方唔係咁輕易就可以重新建立。<br />\n斷捨離呢三個字，唔係得個講，係要做先有效果，而我都相信大家係聰明人，好知道守連儂牆定係守香港先最重要。<br />\n點解成日有其他手足話連儂牆係打飛機，因為呢啲牆同打j，兩者都係單向，唔會得到其他回應。連儂牆遍地開花咁多日，乜有因為咁樣回應過咩？講到呢道，好希望大家明白連儂牆只係我地一撻撻既精液，因為呢個政府，對於如此和平既反抗，係唔會有任何我地期待既反應，呢啲牆喺香港，只係文宣。<br />\n我唔知下一次612，71咁既大型示威係幾時，只願大家養精蓄銳，身體同心理上都好好準備，繼續搞連儂牆，我相當支持，但唔好拘泥於守佢。<br />\n即使忍唔住要守佢，咁無啦啦有人被打，都麻煩先制止主動方，在場幾十個鏡頭影住，有幾個出嚟阻止衝突難道好困難？<br />\n最後想講聲，多謝咁多位手足，場仗未完，我地要繼續打落去。"},{"pid":"3f186e1e8284aebc4be2e0338c837f2cc13faa8b","tid":1308071,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:48:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b24e8e65fc0d0c1912f4c2db41627db200c1e3e9","tid":1308071,"uid":111761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:49:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"734994a53f7ead5a356ad2d9b38d97d1e23bfb2e","tid":1308071,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:53:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"586cd006fff8b6a4f48aced2f09aebe2807708c7","tid":1308071,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:57:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"94aacfbd32f6781b351254e0ca7cfd51c2cbcbd2","tid":1308071,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092892a8e1064e13cfc5719fd705ad82995bbda5","tid":1308071,"uid":15948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T19:59:24.000Z","msg":"玩貼紙唔包比人打<br />\n好好保護自己和同路人啦總之"},{"pid":"56f188b5047e6cf7aa83428982d06fd065984e98","tid":1308071,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:02:47.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"341c119b7d9dfe6354378f9bd7c86ba197b76337","tid":1308071,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:10:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6339d26169c77b4d28409aa6a84ae69f37ae2fe","tid":1308071,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:17:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a319f143044ab9439536808c6a93603ddd960b3d","tid":1308071,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:22:47.000Z","msg":"血小板封路貼傷口，天經地義。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9eAW3P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9eAW3P.jpg&h=7c1a5fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0vP1vv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0vP1vv.jpg&h=79faec23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c35d6eb637860d313942a5363c5afdc9505b389","tid":1308071,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T21:04:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15d5c151c164ba07a566fc0786a53f6bba3f5bf3","tid":1308071,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:01:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82623e0ebd448652db020f9f22351d304e7f4a8c","tid":1308071,"uid":233325,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:17:46.000Z","msg":"咁又唔好將連儂牆同保護香港放係對立面！<br />\n記住連儂牆都係同路人想係社區開花嘅一個方法，其實又真係可以做到文宣工作。<br />\n起牆嘅大家可能唔捨得市民嘅心意被糟踏，但係記住，連最初嘅連儂牆都係那怕一次又一次的清潔，甚至安裝監控攝像頭和安排夜間守衛負責看守，極權政府也無法民眾阻止表達意見，人們對自由的追求還是會在第二天在牆壁顯示出來。所以唔好死守，牆無左，我地仲係團結，就仲會可以起得返！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6cMDa1U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6cMDa1U.png&h=1afa9f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EvNOyff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvNOyff.png&h=586bf084&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00dfe15793e2fec4c2bc8333f89dee5dda543ffa","tid":1308071,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:28:17.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"5428d55b8387fbc1aaf1c733d1e2a2f7b811edcb","tid":1308071,"uid":277551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:33:59.000Z","msg":"講中晒心聲，依家條路行錯哂！<br />\n為左抗爭而埋沒左應有既良知！無左咪再起過！<br />\n只係一個方式去表達，同遊行一樣！<br />\n唔係話衝唔好，但依家確實係唔知衝乜，圍政總？但黎緊遊行係上水九東旺角喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd03b1788078f4a2745d83d089d809fc5ba54aa","tid":1308071,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:35:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6629d83e48c5024269a2b97a44bf9371cf84a4f7","tid":1308071,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:36:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37e5fafc7aa39d8cd7683e20d6eb5f84006406bf","tid":1308071,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:40:46.000Z","msg":"有甚麽逆民的東西就貼貼貼貼貼。貼到佢不見天日。<br />\nMemo係人民自發的告票。<br />\n膠紙係人民自發的手扣和監獄。<br />\n<br />\n【無大台攻略】歡迎來玩民主世界遊戲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299957</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e490f0c4e68dbdfd6d5f3fc148fdab5ffa8f26c7","tid":1308071,"uid":278285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:41:06.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nBe water<br />\n有人搞事就好走<br />\n佢走左我地大不了再貼過十張百張<br />\n唔好令自己或身邊人受傷"},{"pid":"c1e6e541674dcc0dfeacc3c20585c8f3d6a22826","tid":1308071,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:51:30.000Z","msg":"【任務欄】<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306215</a><br />\n任務眾多