k\">https://bit.ly/2xHTxB2</a><br />\n7.21 - 升級 - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306161</a><br />\n7.27 - 光復紅土 還我靜土 - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1303394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1303394</a><br />\n7.28 - 將軍澳遊行(東西夾擊) - <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1299842/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1299842/page/1</a><br />\n7.28 - 港島西遊行(東西夾擊) - <a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3016914/org/ed0ae0d672d875fad5d5985a8c9c28ad.jpg/-MUVIbYEHgRsStyc3rJfPIHi_XEbYJllARl_WgEZf1o?v=w1280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3016914%2Forg%2Fed0ae0d672d875fad5d5985a8c9c28ad.jpg%2F-MUVIbYEHgRsStyc3rJfPIHi_XEbYJllARl_WgEZf1o%3Fv%3Dw1280&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0OoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=6946e955\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3016914/org/ed0ae0d672d875fad5d5985a8c9c28ad.jpg/-MUVIbYEHgRsStyc3rJfPIHi_XEbYJllARl_WgEZf1o?v=w1280</a><br />\n隨時 - 抵制TVB - <a href=\"http://t.me/noTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVBteam&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0OoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=f2aa4297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/noTVBteam</a><br />\n隨時 - 大陸旅客送禮勤 - <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YH16DY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YH16DY&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0OoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=ebec78e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YH16DY</a><br />\n隨時 - 美國聯署 人權民主法案 - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0OoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=249d071b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a><br />\n隨時 - 捐款民調 - <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0OoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=a537d407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n隨時 - 「反送中」民情報告眾籌計劃<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F854&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0OoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=12cedaad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/854</a><br />\n隨時 - 連儂牆"},{"pid":"3b00a00e3ca3d1a79641fe035b0958df9eab4c55","tid":1308071,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T22:52:59.000Z","msg":"咪撚守連儂牆啦，好嘉年華<br />\n仲要大大個據點棟喺度俾人攻擊，浪費緊大家心力<br />\n<br />\n守香港，力爭五大訴求，要市民vs政府<br />\n唔係守連儂牆，守護memo，變成市民vs市民"},{"pid":"4fef63a9d24a08cdd767f9549ab3d228d9875c4a","tid":1308071,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T23:30:21.000Z","msg":"[五毛分化警示] 散佈失敗論，叫人聚焦，放棄其他野，去金鐘，乃一貫分化技倆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306283</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔守唔硬碰冇問題，但我唔撚明點解有人借機帶風向，話唔好再搞連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304714\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日突然多左好多風向話區區遊行無用，連儂牆無用，其實咁先代表佢地仲係好有用，大家唔好中計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n對連儂牆既一啲諗法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304579\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304579</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［置頂，極緊要，極長文］唔好再話連儂牆無用也也也，連儂牆甚至可能係呢一場運動既致勝關鍵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n共產黨其實怕我地搞地區工作多過出金鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304935\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304935</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cbd61848573841e89452df38a45b2413b756e863","tid":1308071,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88259f365d7e5ffc4953b235e13b61dd4246175f","tid":1308071,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T14:55:50.000Z","msg":"push"}]}